2009 TAG TEAM LEAGUE
IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE

THE DRAGONS
ARIEL x & WENONA
Combined HT:131”
Combined WT: 235lbs
Season Record:(2-0)
Franchise Record (2-4)

TEAM ICE
Hollie & Bella Rossi
Combined HT:132”
Combined WT: 305lbs
Season Record:(0-2)
Franchise record (3-3)

Welcome to Ultimate Surrender’s 2009 Tag Team League. The Dragons vs Team Ice. Four girls, non-scripted, real tag team action.

The Dragons are undefeated, healthy and look unstoppable. They are the lightest and smallest tag team in the league. Who says size matters?

Team Ice: This team says size matters: they are the big bullies of US. No team outweighs them and every team fears them. However as a team they have yet to win a match, so this is a must win for Team Ice.
title: LIVE TAG TEAM LEAGUE The Dragons (2-0) vs Team Ice (0-2)
